<script>
  let userRole = window.grafanaBootData.user.orgRole;

  if (userRole != 'Admin') {
    let breadcrumbs = document.querySelector('[aria-label="Breadcrumbs"]');
    let toggle = document.querySelector('[aria-label="Toggle menu"]');
    let markFavoriteIcon = document.querySelector('[aria-label="Mark as favorite"]');
    let shareIcon = document.querySelector('[aria-label="Share dashboard or panel"]');
    //hard coce..
    let headerBlocks = document.querySelectorAll('[data-testid="wrapper"]');

    //hide dom if exists
    if (breadcrumbs){
      breadcrumbs.style.display = 'none';
    }
    if (toggle) {
      toggle.style.display = 'none';
    }
    if (markFavoriteIcon) {
      markFavoriteIcon.style.display = 'none';
    }
    if (shareIcon){
      shareIcon.style.display = 'none';
    }

    if (headerBlocks.length > 0) {
      //keep dom's space
      headerBlocks[1].style.visibility = 'hidden';
    }
  }
</script>

targets.rawSql:
select
  mainlineno as workcenter,
  line_type as linetype
from
  qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl
where
  fact_no_merge = '$factory'
  and mainlineno = '$sec_no'
  and "enable" = 'Y'
group by
  mainlineno,
  line_type;

select
  concat('P', d.process_group) as name,
  --       avg(pass_qty / inspection_qty * 100) AS value_avg,
  sum(a.pass_qty) / sum(a.inspection_qty) * 100 as value
from
  qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_process b on a.process_id = b.process_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl c on a.fact_no_merge = c.fact_no_merge
  and a.opgroup_id = c.opgroup_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_fact_process d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge
  and b.process_id = d.process_id
  and c.line_type = d.line_type
where
  a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
  and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and a.inspection_qty > 0
  and b."enable" = 'Y'
  and c."enable" = 'Y'
  and d."enable" = 'Y'
  and c.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
group by
  d.process_group;

select
  c.defect_desc as tdName,
  sum(b.defect_num) as tdValue
from
  qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
  inner join qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection_defect b on a.tls_inspection_id = b.tls_inspection_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_defect c on b.defect_id = c.defect_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge
  and a.opgroup_id = d.opgroup_id
where
  a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
  and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and a.process_id = '$process'
  and b.defect_num <> 0
  and c."enable" = 'Y'
  and d."enable" = 'Y'
  and d.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
group by
  c.defect_desc;

select
  mainlineno as workcenter,
  line_type as linetype
from
  qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl
where
  fact_no_merge = '$factory'
  and opgroup_id = '$sec_no'
  and "enable" = 'Y'
group by
  mainlineno,
  line_type;

select
  distinct c.suggest_desc
from
  qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
  inner join qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection_defect b on a.tls_inspection_id = b.tls_inspection_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_suggest c on b.defect_id = c.defect_id
  inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge
  and a.opgroup_id = d.opgroup_id
WHERE
  a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
  and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and a.process_id = '$process'
  and c."enable" = 'Y'
  and d."enable" = 'Y'
  and d.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
order by
  c.suggest_desc asc;

  and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
  and a.bstkd is not null
  and b.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
  and b."enable" = 'Y'
group by
  a.bstkd,
  a.vbeln,
  a.zzmdnam,
  a.article_no
order by
  a.bstkd desc;

targets.rawSql:
select
  defect_desc
from
  (
    select
      sum(b.defect_num) def_qty,
      b.defect_id,
      c.defect_desc
    from
      qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
      inner join qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection_defect b on a.tls_inspection_id = b.tls_inspection_id
      inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_defect c on b.defect_id = c.defect_id
      inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge
      and a.opgroup_id = d.opgroup_id
    where
      a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
      and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}'
      and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
      and a.process_id = '$process'
      and c."enable" = 'Y'
      and d."enable" = 'Y'
      and d.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
    group by
      b.defect_id,
      c.defect_desc
  ) as X
order by
  def_qty desc
limit
  3;

list.definition:
select concat(f.fact_no, '#', f.fact_no, ' - ', f.fact_name)
	from cfg_user a
	inner join (select distinct group_id, user_pccuid from (
		select group_id, user_pccuid from cfg_group_member 
		union all
		select group_id, user_pccuid from cfg_group_mgr cgm 
		) as group_user) b
		on a.user_pccuid = b.user_pccuid
	inner join cfg_group c
		on b.group_id = c.group_id 
	inner join cfg_auth_board d 
		on b.group_id = d.group_id and c.group_id = d.group_id
	inner join cfg_auth_dp_fact e 
		on d.auth_board_id = e.auth_board_id 
	inner join cfg_fact f
		on e.fact_id = f.fact_id  
	inner join cfg_board_dp_fact g
		on d.board_id = g.board_id and f.fact_id = g.fact_id and e.fact_id = g.fact_id  
	inner join cfg_board h 
		on g.board_id = h.board_id 
	where a.user_pccuid = '${__user.login}'
	and a.enabled = 'Y'
	and f.enabled = 'Y'
	and f.fact_no <> '2151'
	and h.enabled = 'Y'
	and h.board_level = 1
	and h.board_gf_id = '${__dashboard.uid}'
	group by f.fact_no, f.fact_name 
	order by f.fact_no, f.fact_name 
;
list.label: Factory
list.name: factory
list.query:
select concat(f.fact_no, '#', f.fact_no, ' - ', f.fact_name)
	from cfg_user a
	inner join (select distinct group_id, user_pccuid from (
		select group_id, user_pccuid from cfg_group_member 
		union all
		select group_id, user_pccuid from cfg_group_mgr cgm 
		) as group_user) b
		on a.user_pccuid = b.user_pccuid
	inner join cfg_group c
		on b.group_id = c.group_id 
	inner join cfg_auth_board d 
		on b.group_id = d.group_id and c.group_id = d.group_id
	inner join cfg_auth_dp_fact e 
		on d.auth_board_id = e.auth_board_id 
	inner join cfg_fact f
		on e.fact_id = f.fact_id  
	inner join cfg_board_dp_fact g
		on d.board_id = g.board_id and f.fact_id = g.fact_id and e.fact_id = g.fact_id  
	inner join cfg_board h 
		on g.board_id = h.board_id 
	where a.user_pccuid = '${__user.login}'
	and a.enabled = 'Y'
	and f.enabled = 'Y'
	and f.fact_no <> '2151'
	and h.enabled = 'Y'
	and h.board_level = 1
	and h.board_gf_id = '${__dashboard.uid}'
	group by f.fact_no, f.fact_name 
	order by f.fact_no, f.fact_name 
;

list.definition:
select concat(c.process_no, ' | ', c.process_desc, '#', c.process_id) as process
	from qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
	inner join qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection_defect b on a.tls_inspection_id = b.tls_inspection_id 
	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_process c on a.process_id = c.process_id 
  	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_fact_process d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge and c.process_id = d.process_id
	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl e on a.opgroup_id = e.opgroup_id and a.fact_no_merge = e.fact_no_merge and d.line_type = e.line_type 
where a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
	and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}' and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
	and a.defect_qty <> 0 
	and c."enable" = 'Y'
	and d."enable" = 'Y'
	and e."enable" = 'Y'
	and e.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
group by c.process_no, c.process_desc, c.process_id 
order by c.process_no asc;
list.label: Process
list.name: process
list.query:
select concat(c.process_no, ' | ', c.process_desc, '#', c.process_id) as process
	from qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection a
	inner join qmgt_rdb.tls_gf_inspection_defect b on a.tls_inspection_id = b.tls_inspection_id 
	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_process c on a.process_id = c.process_id 
  	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_gf_fact_process d on a.fact_no_merge = d.fact_no_merge and c.process_id = d.process_id
	inner join qmgt_rdb.cfg_mes_gf_aopgroupctrl e on a.opgroup_id = e.opgroup_id and a.fact_no_merge = e.fact_no_merge and d.line_type = e.line_type 
where a.fact_no_merge = '$factory'
	and a.inspection_date between '${__from:date:YYYYMMDD}' and '${__to:date:YYYYMMDD}'
	and a.defect_qty <> 0 
	and c."enable" = 'Y'
	and d."enable" = 'Y'
	and e."enable" = 'Y'
	and e.mainlineno = '$sec_no'
group by c.process_no, c.process_desc, c.process_id 
order by c.process_no asc;
